text: Luohe () is a prefecture-level city in central Henan province, China. In 2010, 2,544,266 people lived there. ==Administration== Luohe administers 3 districts and 2 counties. *Yancheng District (郾城区) *Yuanhui District (源汇区) *Shaoling District (召陵区) *Linying County (临颍县) *Wuyang County (舞阳县) Category:Cities in China Category:Henan
title: Luohe
